text: Huang Chiu-chin (born 17 October 1978) is a Taiwanese taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in finweight at the 1995 World Taekwondo Championships in Manila, after defeating Yang So-hee in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
